Effective Date:
25 Dec 2024
Introduction
Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the Quizia: General Knowledge Quiz app.
Information We Collect
Contact Information
Email Address
: Collected for app functionality and is linked to your identity.
User Content
Gameplay Content
: Used for product personalization, app functionality, and analytics. This data is also used for tracking purposes.
Customer Support Data
: Collected through user inquiries and linked to your identity. Used for analytics and app functionality.
Identifiers
User ID
: A unique identifier created for each app install. Used for analytics, app functionality, and product personalization. This data is also used for tracking purposes.
Purchases
Purchase History
: Linked to your identity and used for analytics, app functionality, and product personalization.
Usage Data
Product Interaction
: Used for app functionality, product personalization, and analytics.
Advertising Data
Collected for third-party advertising and used for tracking purposes.
Diagnostics
Crash Data
: Used for app functionality and analytics.
Performance Data
: Used for analytics and app functionality.
Other Diagnostic Data
: Used for analytics and app functionality.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:
Provide, maintain, and improve our app and services.
Personalize your experience.
Analyze usage and trends to enhance app functionality.
Respond to customer support inquiries and improve our support services.
Display relevant advertisements.
Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with third-party partners for the following purposes:
Advertising: To display third-party ads in our app.
Analytics: To analyze user behavior and improve our app.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. However, please note that because our app uses AdMob for monetization, opting out of personalized advertising may affect your experience within the app. While you cannot opt out of all marketing communications, you can manage your ad preferences through your device settings.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy in the app.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
quizia@digigene.com
.
